  <preparation>Mix together sugar, vinegar, salt, lemon pepper, garlic powder and mustard and bring to a boil: 1 minute on high.

Pour over spinach.

Add bacon + about 1/4 cup bacon drippings.  DON'T REHEAT BACON DRIPPINGS.

Toss salad.  Top with green onion + eggs.</preparation>
